moji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dec1402af17bbd3b4cbd48e2ed064664ac5e74d","tid":2262474,"uid":150814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"回復你本來既面目啦，古~羅~咭！"},{"pid":"5292cebd2d2547bd400398e8b73bb6840b27b001","tid":2262474,"uid":62513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00c9a43c260e4b6f87e80dfd9110634fa8f4d803","tid":2262474,"uid":89382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T07:09:46.000Z","msg":"松田"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:52:04.000Z","msg":"你個腦係咪裝屎架"},{"pid":"fc4a7c4f16926baff5321dd1832a9615c9e84d85","tid":2262474,"uid":50642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"你呢個問題問得真係好呀！"},{"pid":"21c8d0d8fd7e61db14bce62b09a53af16029f684","tid":2262474,"uid":130575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:11:55.000Z","msg":"黎啦黎啦黎啦黎啦黎啦<br />\n掂啦掂啦掂啦掂啦掂啦<br />\nXX雷動光"},{"pid":"7851135baad5d0de034fd74fce4ec736efb61b83","tid":2262474,"uid":367552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:21:09.000Z","msg":"雷電交加 轟天烈地 召喚雷皇龍齊格鱗！"},{"pid":"2fadd55b0afe220f1a40e3d904adc998230765d0","tid":2262474,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"恒管極究斬"},{"pid":"f99722319ecc90dd923ba4a8c3f71a2cc4f1094b","tid":2262474,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"解除封印 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}